vote.title: Authorize a resolution designating the property addressed as 2323 Bryan Street, Dallas, Texas as City of Dallas Neighborhood Empowerment Zone No. 18, pursuant to Chapter 378 of the Texas Local Government Code, to promote an increase in economic development in the zone, establish boundaries for the zone, and provide for an effective date - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
